title: Gloria Sinica: Han Xiongnu Wars
description: Gloria Sinica: Han Xiongnu Wars in a stand-along game based on the engine of Mount&Blade, Warband. Members of ShangShiXuan cohere to archaeological discoveries and historic documents to faithfully preset the culture and scenes of an eastern world.
